\pard\sb480\sa120\b\fs36 Cosmetic Dentistry\b0\fs22\par
\pard\sa160 \par
\pard\sa200 Cosmetic dentistry covers any treatment that is primarily aimed at improving how your teeth look \emdash  the shape, colour, proportion, and overall harmony of your smile. It is not one single procedure but a whole category that includes veneers, bonding, whitening, gum contouring, and smile design. Dr. Sezer brings over 30 years of experience in aesthetic dentistry, which means the focus is always on results that look natural, balanced, and genuinely you.\par
\pard\sa200 Improving your smile is not vanity \emdash  for many people it has a real impact on confidence and how they present themselves in the world. The best cosmetic dentistry does not make you look like someone else. It takes what you already have and refines it. Whether you want one small thing fixed or a complete smile transformation, the process always starts with a conversation about what you want and what is actually achievable.\par
\pard\sa100 \par
\pard\sb200\sa100\b\fs26 When Should You Consider It?\b0\fs22\par
\pard\fi-360\li360\sa80 \bullet\tab {\b You avoid smiling in photos:} This is one of the most common things patients say, and it is entirely fixable in most cases.\par
\pard\fi-360\li360\sa80 \bullet\tab {\b Something about your smile has always bothered you:} Even a single chip or one discoloured tooth can dominate your perception of your own appearance \emdash  small fixes make a big difference.\par
\pard\fi-360\li360\sa80 \bullet\tab {\b You are preparing for a major life event:} Weddings, promotions, or simply a new chapter often prompt people to finally address something they have been putting off.\par
\pard\fi-360\li360\sa80 \bullet\tab {\b Your teeth have changed with age:} Teeth naturally wear, shift, and yellow over time \emdash  cosmetic dentistry reverses those effects.\par
\pard\fi-360\li360\sa80 \bullet\tab {\b You want everything assessed together:} A cosmetic consultation looks at your whole smile as a unit, not tooth by tooth, which often reveals simpler, more efficient solutions.\par
\pard\sa100 \par
\pard\sb200\sa100\b\fs26 What to Expect\b0\fs22\par
\pard\fi-360\li360\sa100 1.\tab {\b Smile consultation.} Dr. Sezer listens carefully to what you like, what you do not, and what you are hoping for \emdash  then gives you an honest, experienced perspective on the options.\par
\pard\fi-360\li360\sa100 2.\tab {\b Treatment planning.} A personalised plan is put together that may combine multiple treatments, sequenced in the right order for the best result.\par
\pard\fi-360\li360\sa100 3.\tab {\b Treatment and review.} Work proceeds at a pace that suits you, with a final review to confirm the result meets your expectations before the case is closed.\par
